#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/clock.rst:2
#: 877a67c13df54617a028b45ceba45cdb
msgid "时钟"
msgstr "Clock"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/clock.rst:17
#: de7c16af72484952b50b2bd7fc8725cf
msgid "如果想给某个外设配置一个时钟，需要调用哪些函数？"
msgstr ""
"If you want to configure a clock for a specific peripheral, which functions "
"need to be called?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/clock.rst:19
#: eea24aa3326d4191b59fc698deecd214
msgid ""
"GLB_Set_System_CLK() --> 设置整个系统的时钟， 部分外设时钟也来源于此 "
"GLB_Set_......_CLK() --> 设置目标外设时钟 GLB_AHB_Slave1_Clock_Gate() --> 部"
"分外设时钟默认被gate， 使用该外设时需要主动ungate 其它外设 --> 目标外设内相关"
"时钟配置"
msgstr ""
"GLB_Set_System_CLK() --> Sets the clock for the entire system. Some "
"peripheral clocks are also derived from this. GLB_Set_......_CLK() --> Sets "
"the clock for the target peripheral. GLB_AHB_Slave1_Clock_Gate() --> Some "
"peripheral clocks are gated by default. When using such a peripheral, you "
"need to actively ungate it. Other peripherals --> Relevant clock "
"configuration inside the target peripheral."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/clock.rst:24
#: 7f97d9bc482e44b2b1d396a2bf6c75a9
msgid "PDS、HBN的工作机制是什么？如何实现唤醒？"
msgstr ""
"What are the operating mechanisms of PDS and HBN? How is wake-up implemented?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/clock.rst:26
#: 7361b4b2b6e9413ba0569e198538ac01
msgid ""
"将芯片划分为多个电源域，通过不同电源域掉电与否的组合来实现不同级别的低功耗模"
"式，详情参见低RM功耗章节。 不同级别的低功耗模式唤醒源均不相同。"
msgstr ""
"The chip is divided into multiple power domains. Different levels of low-"
"power modes are implemented through combinations of whether different power "
"domains are powered down. For details, refer to the low-power chapter of the "
"RM. Wake-up sources vary for different levels of low-power modes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/clock.rst:30
#: 6bea23641f874bbebfd011b5feff5d61
msgid "芯片的功耗是多少？"
msgstr "What is the chip power consumption?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/clock.rst:32
#: 9678af03480d439a8ddbe532a48de9ed
msgid ""
"低负荷运行时电流在10mA左右，高负荷运行时电流40mA以上，低功耗模式最低可达2uA左"
"右。"
msgstr ""
"The current is around 10 mA under low-load operation, over 40 mA under high-"
"load operation, and can be as low as around 2 μA in low-power mode."
